        <mxCell id="key-gre-t" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;GRE Tunnel10 + OSPF 100&lt;/b&gt; (P2P, PIM-SM) — one tunnel per Border member to the single DMZ hub; carries the overlay loopbacks (Layers 1–2).&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="1">
