        <mxCell id="key-inject-t" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Campus OSPF 1 underlay injection&lt;/b&gt; — Spines (RR) redistribute DMZ Lo1 (10.100.2.1/32) so Borders can reach the GRE tunnel destination. DMZ Lo0 is deliberately withheld to preserve fall-over integrity.&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="1">
